Auto-Pay on Arrival:
Immediate payment processing when destination is reached
Eliminates payment disputes and delays
Provides cost certainty for customers
Route Integrity Monitoring:
Real-time tracking of route deviations
Automatic detection of unplanned detours
Prevents fare inflation through unnecessary route extensions
Fair Rerouting Compensation:
Legitimate rerouting reasons are validated and approved
Both driver and customer receive bonus tokens (5 ROSE each)
Transparent notification system for all parties
Safety-First Approach:
Drivers can report safety concerns without penalty
System validates rerouting reasons using external data
Encourages safe driving practices
Enhanced Trust:
Automated systems reduce potential for manipulation
Transparent processes build trust between drivers and customers
Bonus tokens incentivize honest behavior
This implementation ensures that Grab A Rose maintains fair pricing, route integrity, and customer satisfaction while providing immediate compensation for legitimate route changes. The system balances automation with human oversight to handle edge cases effectively.
